Anyway, I'm think I've worked out what I have to do on the GUI now with your help above:

- Choose &quot;Set Variable or Attribute&quot;
- SET VARIABLE [Kitchen Door.lockable] = EXPRESSION [false]
- And then, as long as I've set the door as something with a lock, then lockable will be an attribute it knows and that works <!-- s:-) --><img src="{SMILIES_PATH}/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" /><!-- s:-) -->

